Description: Cortex Debug Connector, standard ARM Cortex-M SWD and JTAG interface
Generic connector, double row, 02x25, odd/even pin numbering scheme (row 1 odd numbers, row 2 even numbers), script generated (kicad-library-utils/schlib/autogen/connector/)
ARM Cortex-M4 MCU, 1024KB flash, 192KB RAM, 180MHz, 1.8-3.6V, 82 GPIO, LQFP-100
